** Hayasasurahime
* Tenmangū Shrine
** {{ill|Sugawara no Michizane|ja|Sugawara no Michizane|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* Inari Shrine
** {{ill|Ukanomitama|ja|宇賀御魂神|qq=draft|qq=draft}}

== Cultural Properties ==

=== Important Cultural Properties (National Designation) ===
* Main Hall

=== Other Cultural Properties ===
* Masks and costumes, including a {{ill|Sarutahiko|ja|猿田彦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} mask, a {{ill|Shōjō|ja|猩々|qq=draft|qq=draft}} mask, and a lion dance head, are preserved<ref name="shishi" />.

